{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"93c11a4a4f","title":"中央文革小组关于新华社问题的几点通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"69341fb0cd","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":14,"articleId":"93c11a4a4f","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"中央文革文件","id":"056fc2625f","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"新闻广播和出版","id":"268718f23b","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"69af636182","type":"title","text":"中央文革小组关于新华社问题的几点通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7319953ea","type":"paragraph","text":"1、新华社是党中央领导的宣传机构，不得由社内外的革命群众组织接管。领导机构和人员的调整，要由党中央决定或批准。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffe45063ac","type":"paragraph","text":"2、新华社已经建立的监督小组要切实加以改进，这个问题应由社内的革命群众协商解决，在没有妥善解决之前，都不要进驻社长办公室。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8d5e04f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"3、主持新华社常务工作的副社长王唯真同志有职有权。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e5e2ab4cf9","type":"paragraph","text":"4、立即成立临时工作小组，由六人组成，协助王唯真同志工作。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d844376563","type":"paragraph","text":"5、一切工作同志都要坚守岗位，遵守纪律，抓革命促生产，保证完成党和国家的任务。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b1effef458","type":"paragraph","text":"6、关于规章制度问题可以批评、批判，提出改革建议，但要上级领导机关批准才能执行。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bcd106ffa5","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革小组","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0e9b504d8e","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年二月十四日","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93c11a4a4f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}